OL,5, A deposit-free mortgage specifically   
OL,6, aimed at people currently renting has  
OL,7, been launched by a UK building society.
OL,9,FWhile a handful of other no-deposit    
OL,10,Fdeals are available, they all need the 
OL,11,Ffinancial backing of family or friends.
OL,13,FSkipton Building Society says while its
OL,14,Fdeal requires 12 months of on-time     
OL,15,Frental payments and a good credit      
OL,16,Fhistory, it does not need a guarantor. 
OL,18,FA campaign group said while no-deposit 
OL,19,Fdeals could help buyers, the lack of   
OL,20,Faffordable homes remains a key problem.
